<p class="">I have just said that I was referring to the Minister of Information, who was appointed two or three days ago, who is a Noble Lord in another House, and who is the Minister responsible for this Department. The Lord Privy Seal is not, as I understand it, responsible for the Department —</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
